9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"Chennai Express | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"Rahul embarks on a journey to a small town in Tamil Nadu to fulfill the last wish of his grandfather: to have his ashes immersed in the Holy water of Rameshwaram. En route, he meets a woman hailing from a unique family down South. As they find love through this journey in the exuberant lands of South India, an unanticipated drive awaits them."}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/106160/chennai-express"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"Chennai Express"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"Rahul embarks on a journey to a small town in Tamil Nadu to fulfill the last wish of his grandfather: to have his ashes immersed in the Holy water of Rameshwaram. En route, he meets a woman hailing from a unique family down South. As they find love through this journey in the exuberant lands of South India, an unanticipated drive awaits them."}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/movies/106160/chennai-express"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/9j7XfhBJKNfidMCa8JsNbqU1waV.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",{"property":"og:type","content":"video.movie"}],["$","meta","10",{"name":"twitter:card","content":"summary_large_image"}],["$","meta","11",{"name":"twitter:title","content":"Chennai Express"}],["$","meta","12",{"name":"twitter:description","content":"Rahul embarks on a journey to a small town in Tamil Nadu to fulfill the last wish of his grandfather: to have his ashes immersed in the Holy water of Rameshwaram. En route, he meets a woman hailing from a unique family down South. As they find love through this jo